SEASON NINE MATCH UP!
SERENA BLAIR
The Jockey

The Thorn

Lifetime record (0-1)

Serena Blair is currently ranked 8th and is one of the best featherweights we have. Today she steps up against a bigger, heavier opponent. Serena has been training off the mat and is in great shape. She is tenacious and at only 5', 105 lbs, Serena is a hell cat to wrestle!
Audrey Rose (Ranked 14th) has yet to win a match. However she has been training two times a week with the same trainer that trains many of our stars. This sexy wreslter is the poster child for sportsmanship.
This was an intense and brutal match up from the first whistle. Both girls got submission holds on their opponent but neither was able to make the other submit. Pure grit and determination won the day, with the loser defeated, humiliated and fucked on the mat like a common whore. Ultimate Surrender, the only non-scripted real wrestling league on the net.
title: Serena Blair (8th) vs Audrey Rose (14th) Brutal fight, neither wanting to lose. Intense action!
